---
<section class="bg-white py-24 md:py-32">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-8 lg:px-8 xl:px-16">
        <div class="lg:h-[calc(100vh-6rem)] grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 lg:grid-rows-[1fr_auto] lg:gap-y-6">

            <!-- Marca -->
            <div class="flex flex-col lg:grid lg:grid-rows-subgrid lg:row-span-2 gap-6 py-12 lg:py-0 lg:pr-6 border-l-2 border-black pl-6">
                <div class="flex flex-col gap-6">
                    <p class="text-xs lg:text-sm text-gray-600 font-medium tracking-wide">— Identidad</p>
                    <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl xl:text-5xl font-semibold leading-none tracking-tight">Marca</h2>
                </div>
                <ul class="flex flex-col gap-2 list-none p-0 content-start">
                    <li class="relative pl-4 text-base lg:text-lg xl:text-xl leading-relaxed text-black font-medium before:absolute before:left-0 before:top-[0.55em] before:size-1.5 before:rounded-full before:bg-black/20">
                        Desarrollamos el universo conceptual y creamos la identidad de la marca: nombre, diseño, aplicación y manuales de uso.
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <!-- Comunicación y Contenido -->
            <div class="flex flex-col lg:grid lg:grid-rows-subgrid lg:row-span-2 gap-6 py-12 lg:py-0 lg:px-6 border-l-2 border-black pl-6 mt-12 lg:mt-0">
                <div class="flex flex-col gap-6">
                    <p class="text-xs lg:text-sm text-gray-600 font-medium tracking-wide">— Estrategia</p>
                    <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl xl:text-5xl font-semibold leading-none tracking-tight">Comunicación<br/>y Contenido</h2>
                </div>
                <ul class="flex flex-col gap-2 list-none p-0 content-start">
                    <li class="relative pl-4 text-base lg:text-lg xl:text-xl leading-relaxed text-black font-medium before:absolute before:left-0 before:top-[0.55em] before:size-1.5 before:rounded-full before:bg-black/20">Diseñamos y gestionamos planes de comunicación integral: diagnóstico, estrategia, creatividad y manual de comunicación.</li>
                    <li class="relative pl-4 text-base lg:text-lg xl:text-xl leading-relaxed text-black font-medium before:absolute before:left-0 before:top-[0.55em] before:size-1.5 before:rounded-full before:bg-black/20">Administramos e implementamos la comunicación en plataformas digitales y medios tradicionales.</li>
                    <li class="relative pl-4 text-base lg:text-lg xl:text-xl leading-relaxed text-black font-medium before:absolute before:left-0 before:top-[0.55em] before:size-1.5 before:rounded-full before:bg-black/20">Implementamos campañas 360°.</li>
                    <li class="relative pl-4 text-base lg:text-lg xl:text-xl leading-relaxed text-black font-medium before:absolute before:left-0 before:top-[0.55em] before:size-1.5 before:rounded-full before:bg-black/20">Desarrollamos sitios web sostenibles.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <!-- Consultoría -->
            <div class="flex flex-col lg:grid lg:grid-rows-subgrid lg:row-span-2 gap-6 py-12 lg:py-0 border-l-2 border-black pl-6 mt-12 lg:mt-0">
                <div class="flex flex-col gap-6">
                    <p class="text-xs lg:text-sm text-gray-600 font-medium tracking-wide">— Impacto</p>
                    <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl xl:text-5xl font-semibold leading-none tracking-tight">Consultoría</h2>
                </div>
                <ul class="flex flex-col gap-2 list-none p-0 content-start">
                    <li class="relative pl-4 text-base lg:text-lg xl:text-xl leading-relaxed text-black font-medium before:absolute before:left-0 before:top-[0.55em] before:size-1.5 before:rounded-full before:bg-black/20">Identificamos y desarrollamos planes y modelos de negocio.</li>
                    <li class="relative pl-4 text-base lg:text-lg xl:text-xl leading-relaxed text-black font-medium before:absolute before:left-0 before:top-[0.55em] before:size-1.5 before:rounded-full before:bg-black/20">Elaboramos diagnósticos de triple impacto (social, ambiental y económico) para productos, proyectos y empresas.</li>
                    <li class="relative pl-4 text-base lg:text-lg xl:text-xl leading-relaxed text-black font-medium before:absolute before:left-0 before:top-[0.55em] before:size-1.5 before:rounded-full before:bg-black/20">Diseñamos e implementamos estrategias de impacto positivo.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

        </div>
    </div>
</section>
